rows.label: qst700504_msg0001
rows.name:
It's finally done! Thank you,
you've been a great help.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0002
rows.name:
...So, sorry to ask right
away, but can you spare
some time after this?

rows.label: qst700504_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to introduce you
to the client. I just saw
him in the courtyard.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0004
rows.name:
I can't really say I made
it myself, so just for a
little while, please?

rows.label: qst700504_msg0005
rows.name:
...It's not that I think
meeting the client alone
would be tiring or anything.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0006
rows.name:
All right, I'll be waiting
in Sachsum Gardens. Don't
forget to come, okay?
